criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion criteria: (a) diagnosis of BPD according to DSM-IV-TR criteria; (b) age between
        20 and 50 years; (c) heavy use of MHS during the year before the study - as defined below;
        and (h) signed informed consent.

        Exclusion Criteria: (d) acute full-syndrome Axis I disorder requiring urgent inpatient
        treatment; (e) current Substance Dependence Disorder; (f) moderate to severe Mental
        Retardation; (g) previous treatment with structured psychotherapy;
